com.vtls.opensource.formats
Interface FormatProperties

All Known Implementing Classes:
AudioProperties, ImageProperties, JPEG2000Properties, JPEGProperties, MediaProperties, MicrosoftDocumentProperties, MrSIDProperties, PDFProperties, XMLProperties
public interface FormatProperties

This interface provides the property names and functions for Property extended classes representing the useful information for files in different formats.
